{"tid":414770,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"聰明做得快vs勤力做得多 邊個上位快？","createTime":"2017-09-26T13:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T00:25:55.000Z","uid":39866,"like":128,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d36a9a1f5d283ca3d715ba62481c494b1651d6a0","tid":414770,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:02:33.000Z","msg":"假設有兩個人 辦工時間9至6<br />\n當普通人每日可以做80個task<br />\n<br />\nA每日準時返準時走<br />\n食飯前後一個鐘都會hea<br />\n佢一日可以做100個task<br />\n<br />\nB每日早半個鐘返 每晚9點先走<br />\n通常帶飯好快食完就會繼續做野<br />\n佢一日可以做110個task<br />\n<br />\n邊一個上位會快d?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聰明做得快<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勤力做得多"},{"pid":"7a01f9eedf43536ced037230f7c22bfd64728ca1","tid":414770,"uid":72085,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:07:29.000Z","msg":"講真，呢個真係睇公司文化&amp;行業<br />\n鬼佬公司+創意產業 你做1000個task 都唔及1個idea<br />\n<br />\n相反華人公司 + 古板行業 你醒到識飛天都冇用，見到你做野=有做野"},{"pid":"58bab55fdfeadaab57a096c2ecf6e028899541a8","tid":414770,"uid":102651,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"係香港肯定係後者！老細點會想請個醒目仔番黎有機會同自己唱反調？最好就請牛隻番黎，又唔會搏咀，瘋狂要佢ot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2915d1d57297367604a15a8d3646d97379baf6","tid":414770,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"又快又多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5422468d5786dc150b54279ee6ee3020bc90fea4","tid":414770,"uid":60287,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"隔離日日刷鞋打小報告果個"},{"pid":"24ed21344ba720078c9d0400da748128e060cbd8","tid":414770,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:11:22.000Z","msg":"做得快無著數，deadline前交到就得"},{"pid":"8b097f1e0fa4ba97e9fb1e083afe980b7dae1176","tid":414770,"uid":54371,"like":1,"dislike":